<section class="about-section info-section" data-scrollax-parent="true">
	<figure class="figure" data-scroll data-depth="0.7" data-mobile_speed="6.5" data-scrollax="properties: @figureParallax"></figure>
	<div class="section-content" data-scroll data-depth="1.2">
		<article class="section-article">
			<p>
				Same as any other new thing, <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span> also started as an idea. And although it might sound a bit confusing,
				I genuinely wanted to build a cloud-native web-application deliberately using microservice architecture.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you are wondering the sense behind putting a few general words in such a fancy new way, unfortunately, this is not the right place for it.
				However, I might just give you a hint - <a href="https://martinfowler.com/architecture/#:~:text=Architecture%20is%20about%20the%20important%20stuff.%20Whatever%20that%20is" target="_blank">
					“Architecture is about the important stuff. Whatever that is”
				</a>.
			</p>
			<p>
				Anyway, the thing you should know is that all that you're seeing here was originally
				created as part of my exploration and research of modern technologies and the need behind them.
			</p>
			<p>
				<em>So is it all about sneakers or not?</em>&ensp;Well yes, it totally is! No matter it all started as a small side-project afterwards,
				I use my passion for fashion, especially sneakers, as the soul of a future product as well as an endless source of enthusiasm.
			</p>
			<p>
				As a result, <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span> ends up being a web-based market platform such as <a href="https://www.stadiumgoods.com/" target="_blank">Stadium Goods</a>,
				<a href="https://www.grailed.com/" target="_blank">Grailed</a>,
				<a href="https://www.goat.com/" target="_blank">GOAT</a> or <a href="https://stockx.com/" target="_blank">StockX</a>.
				And even though there are plenty more of these today, eventually <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span> is a completely different type of product.
				Since <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span> is not trying to make any money but on the contrary,
				intentionally promotes other shops by redirecting its user to their websites, directly to the page
				where he\she can purchase a pair of sneakers he\she liked and tried to buy on this website.
			</p>
			<p>
				With that being said, <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span>'s mission is also intended to inspire like-minded enthusiasts to
				also start building things in the quest for a greater, more authentic, and more creative future!
			</p>
		</article>
		<a class="hand-wrapper" href="@handIllustrationCredit" target="_blank" data-direction="1">
			<img class="hand-asset" src=@($"{Environment.FileStoragePath}/assets/hand-air-max-90-5.png") alt/>
		</a>
	</div>
	<a class="window-asset" href="@windowIllustrationCredit" target="_blank"
		data-scroll data-depth="1.3" data-scrollax="properties: @windowAssetParallax">
		<img src=@($"{Environment.FileStoragePath}/assets/window-air-max-97-vapormax.png") alt/>
	</a>
</section>
