<section class="about-section info-section" data-scrollax-parent="true">
	<figure class="figure" data-scroll data-depth="0.7" data-mobile_speed="4" data-scrollax="properties: @figureParallax"></figure>
	<div class="section-content" data-scroll data-depth="1.2">
		>
		<article class="section-article">
			<p>
				The original goal of this whole campaign is, in fact, already fully achieved.
			</p>
			<p>
				I've discovered a crazy amount of new priceless knowledge and valuable experience that is not only useful now but also will make its way to the core for my future projects.
				<br/>
				I've acquired skills of usage and get to know plenty of new, crazy-powerful, groundbreaking technologies
				as well as high-order architectures, design patterns, and paradigms of web services and cloud systems development.
			</p>
			<p>
				So my work here can be called done. However, like any parent wants his child to have a better future,
				I also have hope for <span class="kicksware">Kicksware</span> to become a thing.
			</p>
			<p>
				In order to achieve this, I really could use another hothead to kinda level up the game.
				So if you have some ideas on how to take advantage of this well-designed, built, and pretty much
				ready-to-use platform, then feel free to contact me and I hope together we will make it work!
			</p>
			<p>
				Also if you happen to have your stunning exceptional idea that can put my passion and
				enthusiasm for creating new staff into a truly inspiring and worthwhile direction,
				I encourage you to use the next section of this page in order to help us both!
			</p>
		</article>
		<a class="hand-wrapper" href="@handIllustrationCredit" target="_blank" data-direction="-1">
